Package scheduler

This package contains all of the classes to create our GVSU Scheduler project.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BannerSchedScrapper
    Creates a scraping tool for retrieving HTML elements from Banner.
    Course
    Class to store data about an individual course entry that was pulled from the HTML calendar.
    ICSEventBuilder
    Helps create a list of calendar events in ICS format.
    LoginView
    Creates a login window for students to retrieve their student schedules from Banner.
    MainGUI
    Description: The main GUI that extends the file created by Netbeans called NetbeansGUI.java.
    NetbeansGUI
    This is the Advanced GUI for the Grand Valley Scheduler application.
    Schedule
    Title: Schedule Description: Class to hold information about a schedule.
    Scheduler
    Class that stores a whole schedule full of courses.

Package scheduler Description

This package contains all of the classes to create our GVSU Scheduler project.
Author:
Jacob Walton, Marshal Brummel, Alan Sisophone
